OL,3,CNursery fined after toddler scarred
OL,4,Cfor life by scalding water
OL,6,FA nursery has been fined more than
OL,7,F#20,000 after a toddler was left
OL,8,Fscarred for life by scalding water.
OL,10,FThe girl suffered severe burns to her
OL,11,Fhead, face and neck at The Children's
OL,12,FGarden Day Nursery in Stamford,
OL,13,FLincolnshire, in 2023, when an open
OL,14,Ftopped milk bottle warmer toppled over
OL,15,Fon a worktop.
OL,17,FShe needed specialist hospital
OL,18,Ftreatment as a result of her injuries.
OL,20,FThe nursery admitted two Health and
OL,21,FSafety offences at Lincoln Crown Court.
