OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read in
OL,7,Fcourt, the girl's mum said: "Her scars
OL,8,Fwill be for life, and she will need
OL,9,Fmore surgery and more treatments as
OL,10,Fshe grows up.
OL,12,F"The fact that we handed our daughter
OL,13,Fover, where we felt she was safe is
OL,14,Fwhat we struggle with and the guilt
OL,15,Faround this will not leave us."
OL,17,FProsecutors said the the use of the
OL,18,Fbottle warmer had been risk-assessed,
OL,19,Fbut not sufficiently so.
