OL,6,FIt had been connected to a plug socket
OL,7,Fin a cupboard beneath the counter by
OL,8,Fan extension cable.
OL,10,FJudge Sjolin Knight said the
OL,11,Fcircumstances of how the bottle warmer
OL,12,Fcame to tip over were not totally
OL,13,Funderstood.
OL,15,FShe said: "It is really important that
OL,16,Fincidents like this are fully and
OL,17,Fproperly investigated and prosecuted."
