OL,3,CNursery fined after toddler scarred
OL,4,Cfor life by scalding water
OL,6,FAli Bajwa KC, defending, said the
OL,7,Foperators of the Children's Garden Day
OL,8,FNursery partnership were "mortified"
OL,9,Fthat the bottle heater had inflicted
OL,10,Fsuch horrific injuries.
OL,12,FMr Bajwa said his client had taken
OL,13,Fsteps to ensure the incident could not
OL,14,Fbe repeated, including replacing the
OL,15,Fbottle warmer with one that doesn't
OL,16,Fuse hot water.
OL,18,FSince the incident, South Kesteven
OL,19,FDistrict Council has written to all
OL,20,Fsimilar businesses reminding them of
OL,21,Fthe risks associated with scalding.
